hopobject.body: Insert your card desyrel 100 fiyat He said: "The interesting thing about digital fabrication, of which 3D printer is one technique, is that it actually is the...we often say: it's a CD player of the building industry - so how did CD-player digitalized the music industry, and that's why we now have iPods and now Spotify where we share online and everything is streaming, the building industry is a little bit more conservative at the moment but digitalization can totally transform that industry into a more agile industry as well where you can actually share online and upgrade your neighborhood online, and share world-wide good ideas and then send it to the machine, the fabrication technique which can make a connection between the social networks on one hand and physical making industry on the other hand."
